# User and Group Management Task

## ✅ Group Created
Command: `sudo groupadd devteam`

## ✅ User Created and Added to Group
Command: `sudo useradd -m -s /bin/bash -g devteam vaishnavitest`

## ✅ Password Set
Command: `sudo passwd vaishnavitest`

## ✅ User Added to sudo Group
Command: `sudo usermod -aG sudo vaishnavitest`

## ✅ Directory Created and Permissions Set
Command:
```bash
sudo mkdir /opt/devproject
sudo chown :devteam /opt/devproject
sudo chmod 770 /opt/devprojec
